					successfully has become part of their training; they know 
					how fleeting an opportunity can be. So here's a &quot;second 
					opinion&quot; about the climate diagnosis, the prognosis if 
					untreated, and what treatments might actually fix the 
					climate problemrather than merely delaying civilization's 
					collapse by a few decades. </div>
