		<a href="http://www.amazon.com/Great-CO2-Cleanup-urgent-ebook/dp/B005ZSQAX8/?_encoding=UTF8&s=digital-text&tag=thecalvinbookshe&linkCode=ur2&qid=1326156572&camp=1789&sr=1-19&creative=9325">
