						</a></div>
				</div>
				<div style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 5px; FONT-WEIGHT: bold" dir="ltr">
					<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>What I did back before climate change became so urgent</b>
				
					</font>
					<p><font face="Comic Sans MS">
					<a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3i2zEcwYZzw&feature=email">
					<font size="4">The Evolution of Human Minds</font></a><font size="4">
					</font></font> <font size="2" face="Comic Sans MS"><a target="NEW" href="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0226092038/thecalvinbookshe/"><img height="180" align=right alt="click to order from amazon.com" src="http://www.williamcalvin.com/img/BFAS-160.jpg" width="121" border="1"></a></font></div>
