<TITLE>Perspective of Mind: Douglas Hofstadter</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFEE" LINK="993333" VLINK="333300">
<table width="800" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="center">
<tr>
<td>
<div align="center"><a href="http://www.bizcharts.com/stoa_del_sol/index.html">Home</a>
| <a href="../logos/index.html">The&nbsp;Logos&nbsp;Continuum</a> | <a href="../plenum/index.html">The&nbsp;Cosmic&nbsp;Plenum</a>
| <a href="../imaginal/index.html">The&nbsp;Imaginal&nbsp;Within&nbsp;The&nbsp;Cosmos</a>
| <a href="../conscious/index.html">Consciousness&nbsp;In&nbsp;The&nbsp;Cosmos</a>
| <a href="../initiation/index.html">A&nbsp;Cosmic&nbsp;Initiation</a>
| <a href="../living/index.htm">Living In The Cosmos</a> | <a href="../logostalk/index.html">LogosTalk</a></div>
