<HEAD><TITLE>Peter Suber, "Hunter-Hofstadter Map"</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="black" LINK="#0000D0" VLINK="teal" ALINK="#FF0000">

<font face="Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, Sans serif">

<p><CENTER><STRONG><FONT SIZE="+2">Hunter-Hofstadter Map</FONT></STRONG></CENTER>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE="-1">
<A HREF="/~peters/hometoc.htm">Peter Suber</A>, 
<A HREF="http://www.earlham.edu/~phil/index.htm">Philosophy Department</A>, 
<A HREF="http://www.earlham.edu">Earlham College</A>
</FONT></CENTER>

<blockquote>
<P>This is simply to show where in Douglas Hoftstadter's <b>G&ouml;del, Escher, Bach</b> to find topics covered in Geoffrey Hunter's <b>Metalogic</b>, and <I>vice versa</I>.
</blockquote>

